Part1←{
    ⍝' '~⍨¨¯1↓¨1↓¨↑' '(≠⊆⊢)¨⍵
    data←(1∘↓¯1∘↓)¨¨¯1↓¨' '(≠⊆⊢)¨⍵
    buttons←1+⍎¨¨¨','∘(≠⊆⊢)¨¨1↓¨data

    ⍝ If we take the negation of the target,
    ⍝ we get a starting position that we can
    ⍝ iterate on until we have all ones
    start←⊃¨'.'=1↑¨data

    ⍝ The ↑ below adds a bunch of 0 only button configs,
    ⍝ but since they're no-ops, they make no difference
    ⍝ to the outcome
    FlipLights start,↑buttons
}
